Description: Carrara Marble is a prestigious white to blue-grey marble quarried in the Carrara region of Italy. This timeless natural stone has been used since ancient Roman times and remains one of the most sought-after materials for luxury interiors. Its distinctive veining patterns ensure that every slab is unique.
application:
Kitchen countertops
Bathroom vanities
Flooring 
Wall cladding 
Blacksplaches
Fireplace surrounds
Sculpture & Art
